{
  "stem": "21437.1",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "You know, I could sense because she was preparing-- she was around-- she created an atmosphere in preparing the Shabbat.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So when I stood next to her when she was lighting the candles, there was already an atmosphere prepared to welcome the Shabbat.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I felt the peace descending on me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So whatever happened during the-- the week, it just fell away.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And as a matter of fact, now when I talk about it, I've got a four-year-old granddaughter.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And when she comes here in the beginning and I lit the candles, and she put her little hand on my arm like this when I lit the candle.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And as-- I asked my daughter, Helen, what is she doing?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She said, Mom, this is what-- what she's being taught.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So she is putting the hand for her to feel it as well, for her to-- to-- to soak it up, you know?",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So each time I-- I light the candle, she-- she will like guide my hand.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I wasn't doing this.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But-- but I felt-- I felt this.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Until today when I light the candles, I feel the same peace around me.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "No matter what happened before in the home-- at home, no matter how it looks.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There is total peace for when I light the candles and for later on.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Good.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
